{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_02_01_short",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 オーディション結果 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（以前応募した、ミュージカルの）\n（オーディション結果が返ってきた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Audition results)\n(for that musical are out.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おめでとう、合格だったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations‚ you got the role!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？\nまさか受かるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure?!\nI didn’t think I would make it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "通ればいいなとは思ってたけど、俺も驚いたよ\n改めて資料を確認してくれるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m surprised too‚ even though I was hoping for it.\nHere‚ check the details.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5407821334898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私の役は、主人公に恋をする真面目な淑女……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see… my role is an upper-class girl with a serious nature‚ who falls in love with the hero…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 99.99999999999787,
          "startTime": 18.133333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "主演でこそないが、セリフの多いやりがいのある役だ\n沙季の丁寧な話し方や歌い方が評価されたようだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a good role. She’s not a main character‚ but she has plenty of lines.\nLooks like they liked your dignified and polite style of talking and singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "こんないい役をいただけるなんて……とっても光栄です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s an honor… to get such a role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どうする？　受かったのはいいが\n次のライブともぶつかるし、よく考えてくれていいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think? Passing the audition is nice‚\nbut it’ll clash with your next live. Take your time to think about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、ぜひやらせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "こんな貴重な機会を逃したら\n次はいつチャンスを掴めるか分かりませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who knows when the next opportunity will come\nif we let this one pass by?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか。分かった、先方に伝えておく\n細かい連絡はまた後日するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very well. I’ll let them know.\nI’ll send you the details later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "精一杯やらせていただきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll give my all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}